title: The Legend of Sachin Tendulkar (gnv64)
description:
The Legend of Sachin Tendulkar
India Today Commemorative Issue
English | PDF | 33 pages | 36.7 mb
scanned to PDF by me.

THERE HAVE BEEN NATIONAL HEROES BEFORE SACHIN TENDULKAR AND THERE WILL BE PAN-INDIAN SUPERSTARS AF TER HIM. BUT NO ONE ELSE, AT LEAST IN OUR TIMES, GAVE US MOMENTS THAT DEFINED OUR LIVES.

One of India's cricketing icons - Sachin Tendulkar - retired from international cricket recently after the home series with the West Indies. On this occasion, famed Indian current affairs weekly magazine India Today brought out a Commemorative Issue. I have scanned the cover article from the same. It has partial OCR.
